{"tid":1165370,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 到底係我個fd小氣定我𢦀鳩？","createTime":"2019-05-21T17:54:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-22T01:30:15.000Z","uid":91714,"like":31,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"90763cfaaebd9ffe2d4afb6c377988f6ee8c4cb4","tid":1165370,"uid":91714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T17:54:57.000Z","msg":"大家有冇d好少嘢就嬲既fd？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n前嗰排佢<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">突然主動</span></span>搵我想我幫佢d嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你當係workshop咁樣嗰d，因為我識人幫佢報就唔洗錢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上兩個星期已經同佢confirm咗日期時間，佢都話曬ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到今日我提佢記得聽日5點要去喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢又突然話有冇得早d，話想2點半<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n哇我屌你老母，以為自己話曬事咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之前又話okok乜都得咁<br />\n咁我梗係話唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢又話ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後同佢吹多兩句，用對話形式表示啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />=佢 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 要溫書好忙要exam啊 想今個sem過3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(佢嗰科基本上好難唔過3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />身邊班友鳩讀都過)<br />\n<br />\n我: 你嗰科咁易都唔過3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 吓 好chur喎<br />\n<br />\n我: 但你間U呢科都唔勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />((講事實<br />\n<br />\n之後佢就黎料了，開始講自己間U幾勁，再踩埋我間U幾廢，話我有咩資格話佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 你間U冇嘢勁添啦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 我間U起碼個名好聽。你有咩資格話我？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你再係咁講嘢聽日我唔去。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我內心？？？？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個發展太快我都講唔到嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我以為朋友之間互笑下大家垃撚圾又走堂、留名睇你今個sem唔過2，好平常？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我: 吓。。。我講事實啫。。。其實你去唔去都唔關我事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />((真心成件事與我無關⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: ok bye。<br />\n<br />\n我: 但我朋友留咗位比你了。。。你唔去會麻煩到人的。。。。<br />\n<br />\n跟著冇覆<br />\n<br />\n我: 覆一覆啊，你去唔去都同我講聲🙏🏻<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 咪同你講咗我唔去囉。你覺唔覺得自己好過份。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我真係，吓？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n心入面除咗屌你老母唔知講咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我真係覺得好撚on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個人要自卑到咩程度先會比人講一講就嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好撚小學雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">我都有諗過佢係突然去唔到/唔想去就鳩搵d嘢扮下嬲就可以卸曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樓主個fd𢦀鳩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樓主唔啱，咁講嘢"},{"pid":"36e060c461ff533c983c48872942efd5148f6078","tid":1165370,"uid":8138,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T17:56:23.000Z","msg":"唔撚知啊<br />\n絕交啦屌"},{"pid":"0fff95f6005f08c56acaa9d22e385d79b6a62ba3","tid":1165370,"uid":78386,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T18:00:12.000Z","msg":"樓豬個fd靚女就你唔啱<br />\n樓豬個fd唔靚就佢on9"},{"pid":"efbdee71250259b12759e93142ff4b27e4cb2010","tid":1165370,"uid":24455,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T18:02:35.000Z","msg":"樓主小氣d<br />\n啖氣頂住上來開post"},{"pid":"3f2ebfe2911a5ba7e92506a76676caaccf5bddc9","tid":1165370,"uid":223347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T18:02:50.000Z","msg":"兩個都係on9"},{"pid":"e2d44f3ebfb800b9dd7af653f671746909bbbccb","tid":1165370,"uid":91714,"like":1,"dislike":26,"score":-25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T18:03:48.000Z","msg":"我係心入面屌咗佢一千幾百次<img src=\"/assets/fac